{"h31ea8a24g32ddg4e8fg89cdgd7078d2f4263": ["Vicious - and I can't blame them. I'd have done the same if you'd interrupted me in that position.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "ce1e6f0d-9775-541e-f726-a9fc10d8a6f4"], "h8fc8d68cg7f99g4a31g91d3g8bae884396ac": ["Vicious foes make for compelling victories.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "20d649ed-7c03-9f08-600a-dd51054797c1"], "hf2203378geb0cg4977gac5bg78335a0ada51": ["Yes, a fine battle - good exercise for the wits and muscles.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "1fbc018d-4356-2c57-792d-40ce5cfaa961"], "h56400e50g0819g422dga638gf47b5e815485": ["Win enough, and you will soon lack in neither.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "767c3faa-1cf3-8134-94ef-02a5ba1324a1"], "h8628f7d2g1c4fg4ce7g8c09gff5031175fc8": ["We should have left them alone. Those creatures were no threat to us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "b8e70ac9-fbe5-f016-cbec-0e5ae389772f"], "h7afa9f85g2ad7g436bg9ee8g0867b902830d": ["Then take comfort in knowing they died doing something they loved.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "26019122-eebb-abdd-68ff-cd51555c0d36"], "ha26629deg0197g433bg881dg55be141ef8b4": ["Really? Remind me not to barge into your tent.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "2d3c76cc-eaf3-ec29-a63c-59d28adb26f1"], "h3ff61fc9ge867g41bbgb100g1610df8cdfc2": ["Or perhaps you might earn an invitation.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "165f8850-c5e2-fad3-4135-4240872fd9fb"], "hb828e7b8g6b6fg4ba0ga387g3f81b41b58ec": ["Time will tell.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "0b857614-864f-8563-6108-40a8d6e0492c"], "h5dd866a0gdff0g4a9dg8bc3g0bdaa430a108": ["<i>Smile, imagining intimacy with Lae'zel.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "213406e3-b110-d4b0-e020-c0efea680425"], "h61227dfcga7ffg428cg9925g6921f915c4cb": ["I know this look. You might yet earn an invitation to my bunk.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "6154ecac-2c42-809a-a96d-a630ab959782"], "h894cf685ga232g4d5cgb233g6a8b0920537f": ["Well, um - all right then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "5b67f37a-b902-1354-6d8d-ee6c3b303b1e"], "h3cfaadb9ge3c6g48aag8405g8a5d07d8d053": ["Oh - does such talk make you uncomfortable?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "78a43e73-2f38-2e19-0628-cf66a9edf869"], "hb24c36bdgb043g4df2gb227g07e33af20bb4": ["I'll refrain from detailing my conquests, lest you die of embarrassment.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight_Laezel.html", "0cecc7a0-09af-4df2-41f1-79a09aa05fa5"]}